OL,3,CMan jailed for stealing #397,000 from
OL,4,Cfamily firm to go on luxury trips
OL,6,FA man has been jailed for eight years
OL,7,Fin Jersey after stealing #397,000 from
OL,8,Fhis wife's small family business to
OL,9,Ffund a "lavish lifestyle" of Caribbean
OL,10,Fholidays, five-star hotels, cruises
OL,11,Fand an expensive car.
OL,13,FBenjamin Mitton, 46, took the money
OL,14,Ffrom scrap metal company Hunt Bros Ltd
OL,15,Fbetween March 2015 and July 2019.
OL,17,FThe firm has been running since 1851
OL,18,Fand is one of Jersey's oldest family
OL,19,Fbusinesses, said to have operated on
OL,20,Ftrust for generations.
