OL,6,FHe added that Mitton's in-law, James
OL,7,FHunt, broke down as he could not
OL,8,Funderstand how the company was losing
OL,9,Fmoney.
OL,11,FCommissioner Oldland stated: "In
OL,12,Fresponse, you simply shook your head
OL,13,Fand said, 'You should go home'.
OL,15,F"You knew full well where the money
OL,16,Fhad gone; you had stolen it and
OL,17,Fcarried on stealing.
