OL,3,CMan jailed for stealing #397,000 from
OL,4,Cfamily firm to go on luxury trips
OL,6,F"James felt he had failed his father
OL,7,Fand uncle and this has left him
OL,8,Fdoubting any decision he now makes.
OL,9,FYour behaviour has had a devastating
OL,10,Fimpact on all family members, old and
OL,11,Fyoung.
OL,13,F"The company survived, but the impact
OL,14,Fon the family has been very serious."
OL,16,FMitton did not help the police during
OL,17,Fthe investigation, responding with no
OL,18,Fcomment during interviews.
