OL,6,FHe was found guilty in April on one
OL,7,Fcount of larceny as a servant - a
OL,8,Fworker stealing from their employer -
OL,9,Fand two counts of transferring
OL,10,Fcriminal property.
OL,12,FThe Court heard how Mitton was out of
OL,13,Fwork in 2015 and his wife's family
OL,14,Finvited him to join the company as a
OL,15,Ftrainee supervisor.
