OL,4,Cfamily firm to go on luxury trips
OL,6,FCommissioner Oldland added: "This was
OL,7,Fa small, tight-knit family business
OL,8,Fbuilt on trust. As a consequence, it
OL,9,Fdid not have a robust system of checks
OL,10,Fand balances; it was a cash business,
OL,11,Fwhich means it regularly needed to
OL,12,Fwithdraw cash to pay customers.
OL,14,F"You told the bank a number of lies -
OL,15,Fthat you had set up a business, you
OL,16,Fcreated a false trail."
